    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it were still on the showroom floor. The paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly immaculate example of this model.",
      "price": 49500.0,
